00:45:57.240 --> 00:45:59.140
allotted 3 score and 10.

00:45:59.140 --> 00:46:00.680
But he has lived beyond that.

00:46:00.680 --> 00:46:02.070
Maybe he might be 90.

00:46:02.070 --> 00:46:04.050
And he says, by the
